name: Cherry Nobody
description:
Follow me to make sure you see new poses and Nobodys when I post them. Things move fast on this site, it's easy to miss.

Meet Cherry Nobody, this person doesn't exist. You may think she looks like someone you know, but she isn't. Just the imprecise nature of diffusion. Stylized images were generated using the legendary A to Zovya RPG Artist's Tools model.

If you need a consistent character but don't want a known celebrity, Cherry is your gal. Cherry prefers to have really long bright red hair unless you change your prompts. Lowering the strength helps reduce the redness as well. Her freckles are intentionally light, prompt for more if you like.

Follow me for more of the Nobody family coming soon for 1.5 and 2.1.

Click the zNobody tag for more, or the Nobody tag to see other's contributions.

Do you have requests? I've been putting in many more hours lately with this. That's my problem, not yours. But if you'd like to tip me, buy me a beer. Beer encourages me to ignore work and make AI models instead. Tip and make a request. I'll give it a shot if I can. Here at Ko-Fi
